<paragraph blockId="120.[151,1437,151,753]" pageId="120" pageNumber="121">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,655,681]" pageId="120" pageNumber="121">Etymology.</emphasis>
The name (adjective in the nominative singular case) of the new species is derived from its 
<typeStatus box="[1388,1436,655,681]" pageId="120" pageNumber="121">type</typeStatus>
locality, Yakou.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
